@startuml
actor Developer
participant GitHub
participant "GitHub Actions" as Actions
participant "JDK" as JDK
participant "clang++" as CPP
participant "Maven" as Maven
Developer -> GitHub: push / pull_request
GitHub -> Actions: start workflow
Actions -> JDK: setup Java 17
Actions -> JDK: javac -h native-headers
Actions -> CPP: build libbookingstats.so
Actions -> Maven: mvn compile
Actions -> Maven: mvn test
Maven --> Actions: test result
Actions --> GitHub: CI status
@enduml
